%% StratumHook v4 callback lifecycle
sequenceDiagram
    participant LP as Liquidity Provider
    participant PM as PoolManager
    participant HK as StratumHook

    Note over LP,HK: Pool setup
    LP->>HK: preparePool(params)
    LP->>PM: initialize(poolKey)
    PM->>HK: beforeInitialize
    HK-->>PM: PoolTrancheState + stLP/jtLP

    Note over LP,HK: Deposit
    LP->>PM: modifyLiquidity(+L, hookData: tranche)
    PM->>HK: afterAddLiquidity
    HK-->>HK: mint stLP/jtLP, store TranchePosition

    Note over LP,HK: Trading
    LP->>PM: swap
    PM->>HK: beforeSwap → dynamic fee bps
    PM->>HK: afterSwap → waterfall split, IL EWMA

    Note over LP,HK: Withdraw
    LP->>PM: modifyLiquidity(-L, hookData)
    PM->>HK: beforeRemoveLiquidity → accrue vesting
    PM->>HK: afterRemoveLiquidity
    HK-->>HK: settle senior/junior, return delta adjustment
    HK-->>PM: payout-enforcing hook delta
